### ============================================
### YT-DLP AUDIO SERVER API TESTS
### ============================================

@baseUrl = https://geet-music-backend.onrender.com
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/audio

### ============================================
### 1. GET AUDIO INFO
### ============================================

### 1.1 Get Info - Shape of You
GET {{apiUrl}}/info/3JWTaaS7LdU
Accept: application/json

### 1.2 Get Info - Despacito
GET {{apiUrl}}/info/kJQP7kiw5Fk
Accept: application/json

### 1.3 Get Info - Invalid Video
GET {{apiUrl}}/info/invalid
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### 2. DOWNLOAD AUDIO
### ============================================

### 2.1 Download - Shape of You
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/3JWTaaS7LdU
Accept: application/json

### 2.2 Download - Despacito
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/kJQP7kiw5Fk
Accept: application/json

### 2.3 Download - Blinding Lights
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/4NRXx6U8ABQ
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### 3. STREAM AUDIO
### ============================================

### 3.1 Stream - Replace {fileName} with actual filename from download response
GET {{apiUrl}}/stream/{fileName}
Accept: audio/mpeg

### 3.2 Stream with Range Request
GET {{apiUrl}}/stream/{fileName}
Range: bytes=0-100000
Accept: audio/mpeg

### ============================================
### 4. GET FILE
### ============================================

### 4.1 Get File (Stream)
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/{fileName}
Accept: audio/mpeg

### 4.2 Download File (Force Download)
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/{fileName}?download=true
Accept: audio/mpeg

### ============================================
### 5. DELETE FILE
### ============================================

### 5.1 Delete File
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/file/{fileName}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### 6. STORAGE STATS
### ============================================

### 6.1 Get Storage Stats
GET {{apiUrl}}/storage/stats
Accept: application/json

### ============================================
### 7. COMPLETE WORKFLOW
### ============================================

### Step 1: Get info
GET {{apiUrl}}/info/3JWTaaS7LdU

### Step 2: Download
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/3JWTaaS7LdU
# Copy the fileName from response (e.g., "abc123.mp3")

### Step 3: Stream using the fileName from step 2
GET {{apiUrl}}/stream/8032c128-1fce-43ae-97ce-6a56c7ba3343.mp3

### Step 4: Get file
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/8032c128-1fce-43ae-97ce-6a56c7ba3343.mp3

### Step 5: Delete file
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/file/8032c128-1fce-43ae-97ce-6a56c7ba3343.mp3

### ============================================
### 8. BULK OPERATIONS
### ============================================

### 8.1 Download Multiple
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/3JWTaaS7LdU
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/kJQP7kiw5Fk
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/4NRXx6U8ABQ

### ============================================
### 9. ERROR TESTING
### ============================================

### 9.1 Invalid Video ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/download/invalid
Accept: application/json

### 9.2 Non-existent File
GET {{apiUrl}}/file/nonexistent.mp3
Accept: audio/mpeg

### 9.3 Delete Non-existent File
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/file/nonexistent.mp3
Accept: application/json

